+
+Expected result: 21/21 PASS (voxels exact + features within tolerance).
+
+Acceptance thresholds per layer:
+- Voxel set: exact match (OpenVINO == spconv, including SparseConv3d stride>1)
+- Feature tolerance: `max_abs_err <= max(1e-3, 40 * C_in * K_vol * 1.2e-7 * ref_abs_max)`
