+### 3.6 Accuracy acceptance thresholds
+
+| Test | Metric | FP16 Threshold | FP32 Threshold |
+|------|--------|---------------|---------------|
+| Per-layer SubMConv3d | max_abs_err | <= fp32_bound* | <= 1e-4 |
+| Per-layer SparseConv3d | max_abs_err | <= fp32_bound* | <= 1e-4 |
+| E2E cosine_similarity | cosine_sim | >= 0.99 | >= 0.999 |
+| E2E max_abs_err | max_abs | <= 0.5 | <= 0.01 |
